snippet.title: We. The Revolution - Console Edition Teaser
snippet.description:
We. The Revolution is a story driven game set in blood-soaked and paranoid times of the French Revolution already available on PC, Mac and Linux on STEAM and GOG. Console launch for Nintendo Switch, Xbox One and PlayStation 4 will follow 25th June 2019. 

Nintendo Switch pre-order: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/we-the-revolution-switch/

https://www.facebook.com/wetherevolutiongame/
https://www.fb.com/klabater/
https://twitter.com/klabater
